# Put test WAV files here. This directory is gitignored.
# For evaluation, target a range of acoustic contexts:
#   - clean speech (studio, near-field)
#   - speech + background noise (fan, HVAC, traffic, cafe, TV/radio)
#   - silence / near-silence
#   - clipped audio
#   - short utterances, long utterances
#   - non-speech audio (music, noise-only)
#
# Suggested public sources: LibriSpeech, MUSAN, DEMAND, DNS Challenge datasets.
